347
00:20:32,840 --> 00:20:33,760
Sim.

348
00:20:33,880 --> 00:20:34,840
Handpump.

349
00:20:36,000 --> 00:20:37,520
Esse é o primeiro do mundo...

350
00:20:37,920 --> 00:20:41,040
